1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,509
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,979
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,159
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,399
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,729
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,319
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,609
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,059
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,289
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,709
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,199
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,749
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,169
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,158 --> 00:01:07,999
=No Way! My Bro is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,129
=Episode 15=

19
00:01:11,130 --> 00:01:12,900
I intend to make her my Empress.

20
00:01:13,380 --> 00:01:14,659
What do you all think?

21
00:01:14,660 --> 00:01:16,010
Your Majesty,

22
00:01:16,250 --> 00:01:16,980
I don't think

23
00:01:17,020 --> 00:01:18,420
it's a good idea.

24
00:01:19,130 --> 00:01:20,140
Why not?

25
00:01:20,610 --> 00:01:22,299
Though Consort Nan is virtuous,

26
00:01:22,300 --> 00:01:24,170
she comes from a humble family.

27
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:27,730
Besides, her brother, Gu Bei,
commands the Imperial Guards.

28
00:01:27,820 --> 00:01:28,859
Since ancient times,

29
00:01:28,860 --> 00:01:31,570
have there not been enough cases
of imperial in-laws meddling in politics?

30
00:01:31,690 --> 00:01:33,980
An Empress should be judged
by he character and ability,

31
00:01:34,100 --> 00:01:35,620
not her family background.

32
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,480
As for relatives meddling in politics,

33
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:39,620
that only happens
under weak and incompetent emperors.

34
00:01:39,970 --> 00:01:41,730
Official Li,

35
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:44,260
are you calling me incompetent?

36
00:01:46,050 --> 00:01:46,700
Your Majesty,

37
00:01:46,740 --> 00:01:48,140
I would never dare.

38
00:01:48,540 --> 00:01:50,420
Your Majesty
is a wise and capable ruler.

39
00:01:50,460 --> 00:01:52,980
I've always been loyal to the court.

40
00:01:53,070 --> 00:01:56,099
You claim to speak for the court,

41
00:01:56,100 --> 00:01:58,340
yet you make veiled attacks
on His Majesty

42
00:01:58,350 --> 00:01:59,980
and malign your fellow officials.

43
00:02:00,380 --> 00:02:03,129
Isn't that outright treason?

44
00:02:03,130 --> 00:02:04,609
Gu Bei, that's a baseless accusation!

45
00:02:04,610 --> 00:02:06,650
Your Majesty, that's not what I meant.

46
00:02:06,690 --> 00:02:07,370
Enough.

47
00:02:08,580 --> 00:02:10,370
Choosing an Empress is a family matter.

48
00:02:10,770 --> 00:02:11,900
We'll discuss it no further.

49
00:02:13,210 --> 00:02:13,900
Your Majesty,

50
00:02:14,370 --> 00:02:15,899
even ordinary families

51
00:02:15,900 --> 00:02:17,810
consult their elders before a marriage.

52
00:02:17,980 --> 00:02:19,850
Surely the imperial family
should do the same.

53
00:02:19,930 --> 00:02:21,579
Your aunt, the Princess Royal,

54
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:23,130
has been in seclusion for years.

55
00:02:23,610 --> 00:02:25,810
Why not invite her back

56
00:02:25,930 --> 00:02:27,250
and discuss it with her?

57
00:02:29,930 --> 00:02:33,180
- Please reconsider, Your Majesty.
- Please reconsider, Your Majesty.

58
00:02:37,090 --> 00:02:37,900
Very well.

59
00:02:39,810 --> 00:02:41,650
I'll do as you suggest.

60
00:02:43,210 --> 00:02:45,370
Summon the Princess Royal back
to the capital.

61
00:02:46,980 --> 00:02:47,760
Court is adjourned.

62
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:48,970
Court is adjourned.

63
00:02:49,210 --> 00:02:51,580
- Long live Your Majesty.
- Long live Your Majesty.

64
00:02:55,050 --> 00:02:56,060
Here you go.

65
00:02:57,050 --> 00:02:59,000
(Xiaoyao Beauty Cream)
There's plenty for everyone.

66
00:02:59,900 --> 00:03:01,130
Please come again.

67
00:03:01,430 --> 00:03:02,369
Yes, we still have more.

68
00:03:02,370 --> 00:03:03,210
This way.

69
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:04,139
There's a seat.

70
00:03:04,140 --> 00:03:05,020
This way, please.

71
00:03:06,580 --> 00:03:07,259
You'll have skin

72
00:03:07,260 --> 00:03:09,690
just like Her Highness.

73
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:11,299
This one is our bestseller.

74
00:03:11,300 --> 00:03:12,130
Here you are.

75
00:03:12,580 --> 00:03:13,930
Please come again.

76
00:03:14,050 --> 00:03:14,769
Here you go.

77
00:03:14,770 --> 00:03:15,650
Please come again.

78
00:03:20,580 --> 00:03:24,220
Gu Bei!

79
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:25,460
I'll be back in a moment.

80
00:03:27,770 --> 00:03:28,500
What's wrong?

81
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:31,650
My arms are worn out.

82
00:03:31,770 --> 00:03:33,299
I'm a princess, you know.

83
00:03:33,300 --> 00:03:34,930
You've got me working like a servant.

84
00:03:35,370 --> 00:03:36,369
Of course not.

85
00:03:36,370 --> 00:03:37,650
Your Highness,

86
00:03:38,020 --> 00:03:38,979
business is booming,

87
00:03:38,980 --> 00:03:41,300
which just proves
how popular you are, right?

88
00:03:42,610 --> 00:03:43,930
I've heard

89
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:46,060
my brother plans to make Gu Nan Empress.

90
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:47,620
When are you going to give me

91
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:49,609
an answer about us?

92
00:03:49,610 --> 00:03:50,620
Yes. I will.

93
00:03:50,980 --> 00:03:51,530
I will.

94
00:03:52,530 --> 00:03:55,809
He said he wants to make her Empress,
but he hasn't done it yet.

95
00:03:55,810 --> 00:03:57,739
Besides, there's still opposition in court.

96
00:03:57,740 --> 00:04:00,280
Chancellor Hu said they should wait
until the Princess Royal returns.

97
00:04:00,530 --> 00:04:01,130
By the way,

98
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:02,930
what's the Princess Royal like?

99
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:04,410
Will she support His Majesty?

100
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:09,209
My father

101
00:04:09,210 --> 00:04:10,419
only had one sister.

102
00:04:10,420 --> 00:04:11,489
The Princess Royal.

103
00:04:11,490 --> 00:04:13,780
I hardly saw her growing up.

104
00:04:13,930 --> 00:04:15,410
I just remember

105
00:04:15,490 --> 00:04:17,410
she was devoted to Buddhism

106
00:04:17,650 --> 00:04:19,970
and often left the palace
for spiritual retreats.

107
00:04:20,530 --> 00:04:21,970
A Buddhist?

108
00:04:23,090 --> 00:04:24,850
Then she should be pretty reasonable.

109
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:36,400
Aunt,

110
00:04:37,020 --> 00:04:38,340
greetings.

111
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:43,379
(Xiao Zhaoning, Princess Royal of Jing)

112
00:04:43,380 --> 00:04:44,460
You're here, Your Majesty.

113
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:45,650
Have a seat.

114
00:04:52,090 --> 00:04:53,220
It's been years.

115
00:04:53,290 --> 00:04:54,460
You seem much thinner

116
00:04:54,620 --> 00:04:55,900
than before.

117
00:04:55,940 --> 00:04:57,140
Have you been well?

118
00:04:57,170 --> 00:04:58,090
Don't worry, Aunt.

119
00:04:58,580 --> 00:04:59,610
I'm doing well.

120
00:05:01,850 --> 00:05:03,050
Your room seems

121
00:05:03,210 --> 00:05:04,970
a little too plain.

122
00:05:05,170 --> 00:05:06,760
I'll have someone bring
a few decorations.

123
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:09,530
Most people ask for nothing more
than three meals a day.

124
00:05:09,730 --> 00:05:12,380
Wealth and glory are but superficial.

125
00:05:12,850 --> 00:05:13,970
This is more than enough.

126
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:14,940
I'll remember

127
00:05:15,140 --> 00:05:16,460
your teachings, Aunt.

128
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:19,260
While I was on my way back here,

129
00:05:19,330 --> 00:05:20,530
I heard

130
00:05:20,900 --> 00:05:22,460
you plan to appoint an Empress.

131
00:05:25,090 --> 00:05:25,780
That's right.

132
00:05:27,020 --> 00:05:28,409
I wish to make Gu Nan Empress.

133
00:05:28,410 --> 00:05:30,170
However, many at court oppose it.

134
00:05:30,770 --> 00:05:31,490
So

135
00:05:32,290 --> 00:05:33,819
I'd like to hear your thoughts.

136
00:05:33,820 --> 00:05:35,289
If so many oppose it,

137
00:05:35,290 --> 00:05:38,170
why are you so determined
to choose Gu Nan?

138
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:39,850
Because I love Gu Nan.

139
00:05:40,580 --> 00:05:41,379
And Gu Nan

140
00:05:41,380 --> 00:05:42,820
truly loves me.

141
00:05:45,140 --> 00:05:46,380
In the imperial family,

142
00:05:46,410 --> 00:05:48,220
schemes and suspicion are all too common.

143
00:05:48,380 --> 00:05:49,579
A bond like yours

144
00:05:49,580 --> 00:05:50,700
is rare indeed.

145
00:05:50,970 --> 00:05:52,260
Your marriage

146
00:05:52,290 --> 00:05:54,730
should be your own decision.

147
00:05:54,940 --> 00:05:56,220
In that case,

148
00:05:56,650 --> 00:05:57,820
I have every reason

149
00:05:57,940 --> 00:05:59,340
to support you.

150
00:06:00,850 --> 00:06:01,530
Thank you,

151
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:03,410
Aunt.

152
00:06:03,650 --> 00:06:05,140
On my way back,

153
00:06:05,170 --> 00:06:07,940
I heard all of the reforms
you've introduced.

154
00:06:08,330 --> 00:06:09,579
The people say

155
00:06:09,580 --> 00:06:11,610
Jing has finally found a wise ruler.

156
00:06:11,700 --> 00:06:12,780
You're too kind, Aunt.

157
00:06:13,900 --> 00:06:15,020
As Emperor,

158
00:06:15,410 --> 00:06:16,970
my duty is to serve the people.

159
00:06:17,260 --> 00:06:18,730
I want everyone in Jing

160
00:06:18,970 --> 00:06:20,490
to have land to farm

161
00:06:20,650 --> 00:06:22,380
and live in peace and prosperity.

162
00:06:24,210 --> 00:06:25,490
You've changed

163
00:06:25,620 --> 00:06:27,460
a lot.

164
00:06:29,210 --> 00:06:31,380
I've carried these prayer beads
for many years.

165
00:06:31,460 --> 00:06:32,340
Now

166
00:06:32,460 --> 00:06:33,940
I'd like you to have them.

167
00:06:34,170 --> 00:06:36,019
Consider them a gift
from the people of Jing.

168
00:06:36,020 --> 00:06:37,169
May Your Majesty

169
00:06:37,170 --> 00:06:38,530
enjoy a long life

170
00:06:38,620 --> 00:06:40,290
and continue protecting
the people of Jing.

171
00:06:48,410 --> 00:06:49,730
I've made my decision

172
00:06:50,170 --> 00:06:51,490
about the Empress.

173
00:06:51,490 --> 00:06:53,120
This matter is no longer open
for discussion.

174
00:07:02,410 --> 00:07:03,220
Your Majesty,

175
00:07:03,580 --> 00:07:05,169
the Western Yi envoys

176
00:07:05,170 --> 00:07:06,769
are already on their way to the capital.

177
00:07:06,770 --> 00:07:08,259
They've sent a diplomatic letter ahead.

178
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:11,040
They request that Your Majesty marry
the Ninth Princess of the Western Yi

179
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:14,089
and make her Empress to seal an alliance
between our two nations.

180
00:07:14,090 --> 00:07:15,619
(To His Majesty the Emperor of Jing,
Respectfully sealed by Princess Royal)

181
00:07:15,620 --> 00:07:17,260
Reject them.

182
00:07:17,460 --> 00:07:18,220
Your Majesty,

183
00:07:18,380 --> 00:07:20,819
the Western Yi borders Jing,

184
00:07:20,820 --> 00:07:23,019
and clashes along the frontier
are frequent.

185
00:07:23,020 --> 00:07:26,290
A marriage alliance
may keep the border at peace.

186
00:07:27,850 --> 00:07:29,820
If they dare invade,

187
00:07:30,290 --> 00:07:33,580
our cavalry will show them
the might of Jing.

188
00:07:34,970 --> 00:07:35,610
Aunt.

189
00:07:36,020 --> 00:07:37,050
What brings you here?

190
00:07:37,210 --> 00:07:38,380
I visited

191
00:07:38,410 --> 00:07:41,820
the Ancestral Shrine today and thought
I'd stop by to see Your Majesty.

192
00:07:41,970 --> 00:07:42,940
I hope

193
00:07:42,970 --> 00:07:44,460
I'm not interrupting.

194
00:07:44,770 --> 00:07:45,940
Please have a seat.

195
00:07:55,700 --> 00:07:58,580
If we agree to marry
their princess today,

196
00:07:58,620 --> 00:07:59,650
what if they demand

197
00:07:59,940 --> 00:08:02,970
one of our cities?

198
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:05,490
Will you hand that over too?

199
00:08:07,020 --> 00:08:08,610
Your Highness,

200
00:08:08,620 --> 00:08:09,619
our spies report

201
00:08:09,620 --> 00:08:11,700
that the Western Yi has massed troops
along the border.

202
00:08:11,730 --> 00:08:13,849
I'm concerned that refusing them outright

203
00:08:13,850 --> 00:08:15,610
would give them an excuse to invade.

204
00:08:15,900 --> 00:08:18,649
No one decides who my Empress will be.

205
00:08:18,650 --> 00:08:19,460
Agreeing for now

206
00:08:19,650 --> 00:08:22,289
could buy us valuable time.

207
00:08:22,290 --> 00:08:24,970
Please reconsider, Your Majesty.

208
00:08:25,620 --> 00:08:28,410
- We ask Your Majesty to reconsider.
- We ask Your Majesty to reconsider.

209
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:36,760
(To His Majesty the Emperor of Jing,
Respectfully sealed by Princess Royal)

210
00:08:46,530 --> 00:08:47,730
You!

211
00:08:49,170 --> 00:08:50,660
Remember this well.

212
00:08:50,810 --> 00:08:52,060
Jing

213
00:08:52,260 --> 00:08:53,770
will never send a princess in marriage,

214
00:08:54,050 --> 00:08:55,250
never pay tribute,

215
00:08:55,930 --> 00:08:57,700
and never bow to another nation.

216
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:09,480
(Xiaoyao Pavilion Specials)

217
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:14,000
(Long Island Iced Tea, Mojito,
Romance of Jing, Screwdriver)

218
00:09:17,100 --> 00:09:18,180
Xiaoyao Cream, please.

219
00:09:22,770 --> 00:09:24,700
We're closed today.

220
00:09:26,900 --> 00:09:28,090
Give me some Xiaoyao Cream.

221
00:09:28,340 --> 00:09:30,460
You're a man. Why do you need it?

222
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:34,580
What's your problem?

223
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:37,370
- Fushou Cream?
- Fushou Cream?

224
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:39,319
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

225
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:41,719
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

226
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:47,159
♪The brainy emperor plots the strategy♪

227
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:51,519
♪The slacker general leads the charge♪

228
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:53,919
♪Swords clash and warhorses thunder♪

229
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:56,479
♪Let the history judge our deeds♪

230
00:09:56,480 --> 00:10:02,159
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

231
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:07,720
♪Peace across the land, carefree at last♪

232
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:14,040
♪Funny moments never stop♪

233
00:10:14,680 --> 00:10:16,880
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

234
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:21,239
♪Yet through every up and down♪

235
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:23,200
♪We create miracles♪

236
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:25,960
♪From naive youths♪

237
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:28,719
♪To legendary heroes♪

238
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:30,639
♪This journey♪

239
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:34,679
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

240
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:37,200
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

241
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:42,560
♪Let's create♪

242
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:52,520
♪A legend of our own♪

